window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I've awoken in another reality, one where confinement and brutality are a thing of the past.</b></p> <p>I now know freedom, I know compassion, and I know there's something more for me in this f----d up world.</p> <p>Ryker, Axel, Gray, and Emmett. These men, these Ruthless Brothers, have given me strength, and my instinct to run dwindles with each passing day.</p> <p>My past and present are on a collision course set on destruction. While truths have been revealed, nothing can fully prepare you for an evil that never sleeps.</p> <p>All Hell has broken loose, and the Devil is on our doorstep. But I'm ruthless to the core, a rebel till the end, and I'll protect what's mine till my last breath.</p>"; 
